Crown Paints launched Candis paint in the market as part of its business diversification to address emerging customer needs. According to the company, the interior decorative paint, in keeping with its key values of excellence, innovation and design, ensures the final look is of the highest standard in the market. In attendance were Candis Italy CEO Paolo Nosengo and Crown Paints general manager Abhijit Roy. The event took place at Simba Corp in Westlands, Nairobi, on November 22.